T16TD4400E:337b-3: bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
T16TD4400E:337b-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4400E:337b-5: gzhan gyis mi thub rdzogs sangs rgyas //
T16TD4400E:337b-6: mgon po phyogs gcig bzhugs pa na //
T16TD4400E:337b-7: lha gcig dpa' bo chen po la //
T16TD4400E:337b-9: dge ba don du gnyer ba na //
T16TD4400E:337b-10: lha dang mi rnams so so nas //
T16TD4400E:337b-11: bkra shis dag ni brjod bgyis na //
T16TD4400E:337b-12: bkra shis dam pa gang zhig lags //
T16TD4400E:337b-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
T16TD4400E:337b-14: dge ba don du gnyer ba na //
T16TD4400E:337b-15: lha dang mi rnams so so nas //
T16TD4400E:337b-16: bkra shis rnams ni rjod byed pa //
T16TD4400E:337b-17: de dag bkra shis brjod par bya //
T16TD4400E:337b-18: yul bzang gnas dang grogs mchog dang //
T16TD4400E:337b-19: sngon chad bsod nams byas pa dang //
T16TD4400E:337b-20: sems ni legs par gtad byas pa //
T16TD4400E:337b-21: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:337b-22: sbyin dang shin tu smra ba dang //
T16TD4400E:337b-23: yang dag don la rnam nges dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-2: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-3: byis pa rnams la mi brten dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-4: mkhas pa rnams la brten pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-5: mchod 'os rnams la mchod byed pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-6: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-7: pha ma bsnyen bkur byed pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-8: zhi dang tshangs par spyod pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-9: 'byung po kun la snying brtse ba //
T16TD4400E:338a-10: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-11: sdig pa'i las las ldog pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-12: dge ba'i las la brten pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-13: bag yod pa dang brtag mkhas pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-14: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-15: nga rgyal med dang khengs med dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-16: chog shes mthun pas 'tsho ba dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-17: rtag tu byas pa gzo byed pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-18: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-19: mi smod de bzhin bzod pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-20: 'phags pa rnams dang mthun sbyor ba //
T16TD4400E:338a-21: dus skabs su ni chos nyan pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-22: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-23: le lo med dang mang thos dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-24: chos la legs par rnam nges dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-25: de bzhin sems la rnyog med pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-26: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin ;
T16TD4400E:338a-27: / gang zhig sems can thams cad la //
T16TD4400E:338a-28: byams pa'i sems ni rab bsgom zhing //
T16TD4400E:338a-29: dpag tu med de mi 'khrugs pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-30: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-31: gang zhig 'phags pa'i bden rnams la //
T16TD4400E:338a-32: shes rab mig ni rab sbyangs dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-33: tshul khrims nongs par ma gyur pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-34: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin ;
T16TD4400E:338a-35: /'phags pa'i bden pa mthong ba dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-36: tshangs par spyod pa bsgom pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-38: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-39: gang zhig 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-40: ma rig pa dag rnam spangs pa dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-42: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-43: 'jig rten chos brgyad kyis bskyod kyang //
T16TD4400E:338a-44: gang gi sems ni mi g-yo dang //
T16TD4400E:338a-45: dri med zhi dang mya ngan med //
T16TD4400E:338a-46: de ni bkra shis dam pa yin //
T16TD4400E:338a-47: de dang 'dir ni ci rigs par //
T16TD4400E:338a-49: mkhas pa gang zhig rjod byed pa //
T16TD4400E:338a-50: de la rtag tu bkra shis gyur //
T16TD4400E:338a-51: bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs so /
